title: Neo-Tech Capitalist Self-Help Economic Philosophy
description: Neo-tech is a personal and economic pro-capitalism, Ayn Rand offshoot philosophy by Frank R. Wallace. There are books and backup copies of the old website www.neo-tech.com inside as well as some books and material. This stuff is very valuable, and the writings are genial and they can improve your life by helping you get rid of mysticism and becoming a honest value creator. Spread the word and seed!
